name: Search and Destroy
description:
I created this map to enter the Mapmaking contest, but as I got to realize that my time was nearly up and that I still lacked a lot of trigger- and a small piece of terrainwork I felt like posting the map here.

Feel free to test it out and give me some feedback about it.

You may as well also complete the map, if you feel like it :) Just PM me if you feel for it.
